file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
info:
  title: 'test'
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: http://example.com:1234/global/base/path
  - url: /another-global/base/path
  - url: http://localhost:1234
paths:
  /endpoint:
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                required:
                  - key
                properties:
                  key:
                    type: string
                    enum:
                      - value
  /second-endpoint:
    servers:
      - url: http://example.com:1234/local/base/path
      - url: /another-local/base/path
    get:
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                required:
                  - key
                properties:
                  key:
                    type: string
                    enum:
                      - value
  /third-endpoint:
    get:
      servers:
        - url: http://example.com:1234/endpoint/base/path
        - url: /another-endpoint/base/path
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                required:
                  - key
                properties:
                  key:
                    type: string
                    enum:
                      - value
    post:
      responses:
        200:
          description: ''
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                required:
                  - key
                properties:
                  key:
                    type: string
                    enum:
                      - value
